1
00:01:06,079 --> 00:01:08,000
Why am I imprisoned here?

2
00:01:08,519 --> 00:01:09,040
Daozhi,

3
00:01:09,719 --> 00:01:10,640
you don't remember me?

4
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:11,680
Of course I do.

5
00:01:12,319 --> 00:01:13,799
You've done so many evil deeds,

6
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:15,840
how could I forget?

7
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:27,480
Li,

8
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,439
I've been studying ancient texts.

9
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:33,480
I think

10
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,760
if I remove the spiritual root,

11
00:01:34,959 --> 00:01:36,480
Shen Que might not necessarily die.

12
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:37,760
Is that true?

13
00:01:38,079 --> 00:01:38,840
Back then,

14
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,000
he used the threads of affection

15
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:42,319
to seal your spiritual root in your divine consciousness.

16
00:01:42,519 --> 00:01:43,519
If the spiritual root is extracted,

17
00:01:43,519 --> 00:01:44,719
he may not necessarily die.

18
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:46,280
It might also

19
00:01:46,439 --> 00:01:48,879
cause the threads of affection binding you two

20
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:49,959
to quietly dissipate.

21
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,439
Are you saying

22
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:53,560
he will completely forget me?

23
00:01:53,959 --> 00:01:57,280
All your memories of him over a century will be erased,

24
00:01:58,079 --> 00:01:59,239
and they can never be restored.

25
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:02,760
Shen Que,

26
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:05,079
you've forgotten a lot.

27
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,239
I'll help you remember.

28
00:02:09,599 --> 00:02:10,400
You evil spirit,

29
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,120
unable to win in a fair fight,

30
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,479
you resort to sweet talk.

31
00:02:13,199 --> 00:02:15,159
You dare to deceive me?

32
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,319
Do you really want to kill me?

33
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,719
I'm the Virtuous Prince, Shen Que.

34
00:02:27,319 --> 00:02:29,680
It's my duty to slay evil.

35
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,879
Even if I have to die,

36
00:02:31,879 --> 00:02:33,759
I'll kill you here today.

37
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,280
How about

38
00:02:41,919 --> 00:02:42,800
I help you?

39
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:53,960
Your Highness,

40
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,159
you want my life,

41
00:02:57,719 --> 00:02:58,680
and I've given it to you.

42
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,800
Even if you fight with your life,

43
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,199
you can't kill me.

44
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:05,759
Why doesn't the Soul-Devouring Bone Sword work on you?

45
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,439
What kind of evil spirit are you?

46
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,759
Have you ever seen me do evil

47
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,120
or kill the innocent?

48
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,280
I ask myself,

49
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,800
I've done nothing wrong.

50
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:18,560
I never meant to hurt you.

51
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:21,919
As for you,

52
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:26,639
the demon hunters from Qingdu Temple want to kill you.

53
00:03:27,039 --> 00:03:28,639
You'd better stay in the Demon Village.

54
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,199
If you don't hurt those lesser demons,

55
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,000
they won't bother you.

56
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:48,000
Master,

57
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,680
we suffered heavy casualties

58
00:03:49,719 --> 00:03:51,319
in the attack on the Demon Village.

59
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:52,719
Useless fools.

60
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,280
They're dead.

61
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,360
They don't matter.

62
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,599
Master.

63
00:03:57,879 --> 00:03:59,280
Your incompetence

64
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,919
made me feel happy for nothing.

65
00:04:03,599 --> 00:04:04,520
I'm stupid.

66
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,439
I don't understand what you mean.

67
00:04:06,439 --> 00:04:08,240
Meng Li has become a demon.

68
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:11,240
The Demon Clan is getting rampant.

69
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:14,560
The mortal world will become a hell.

70
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,120
Master.

71
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:18,959
But the Demon Clan didn't kill innocent people.

72
00:04:19,199 --> 00:04:20,759
If we destroy their village

73
00:04:20,759 --> 00:04:22,360
to destroy the Demon Village

74
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,439
because of Meng Li.

75
00:04:23,759 --> 00:04:24,959
Please think twice

76
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,480
and don't make a wrong decision.

77
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,519
The most urgent task now

78
00:04:29,879 --> 00:04:31,680
is not to destroy the Demon Village.

79
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:34,000
My Soul Entity is getting weaker.

80
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:37,959
I must find a new body as soon as possible.

81
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:50,319
I shouldn't have been soft that day

82
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,839
and let you spare his life.

83
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:53,759
It's not his fault.

84
00:04:53,959 --> 00:04:54,879
He wanted to kill you.

85
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,560
yet you still defend him.

86
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,720
Now he only remembers

87
00:04:58,360 --> 00:05:00,240
he's the Virtuous Prince with the Demon

88
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:01,920
Capture Order, determined to slay demons.

89
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:03,360
What's wrong with that?

90
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:04,360
Do you realize

91
00:05:04,959 --> 00:05:05,959
without his memory,

92
00:05:06,439 --> 00:05:08,680
he's no longer the Shen Daozhi who loves you?

93
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:12,240
I understand the situation.

94
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,560
Any discomfort after becoming a demon?

95
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,920
Feelings of losing control?

96
00:05:16,319 --> 00:05:18,560
I'm always worried the demonic power will backfire on you.

97
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,879
The demonic nature is under control.

98
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,959
My mind is clearer

99
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,439
than before.

100
00:05:25,279 --> 00:05:27,600
I used to need the dreamer to be asleep.

101
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:29,680
Now I can enter dreams

102
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:32,120
whenever and wherever.

103
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:33,959
But

104
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:36,879
some abilities remain dormant.

105
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,480
What abilities?

106
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,879
I haven't fully grasped them yet.

107
00:05:41,759 --> 00:05:42,680
No rush.

108
00:05:43,199 --> 00:05:44,000
Rest assured.

109
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:45,800
Fine.

110
00:05:46,839 --> 00:05:48,800
Shen Que can stay in the Demon Village.

111
00:05:49,319 --> 00:05:50,160
I'll keep an eye on him.

112
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:51,160
He won't get hurt,

113
00:05:51,439 --> 00:05:53,240
and he won't hurt you or your kind.

114
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,519
The kids are off to eat.

115
00:06:03,519 --> 00:06:04,160
Okay.

116
00:06:21,199 --> 00:06:22,240
Your Highness.

117
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,240
It's me.

118
00:06:23,399 --> 00:06:24,560
Where are you?

119
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:25,959
I'm trapped in the Demon Village

120
00:06:26,279 --> 00:06:27,319
by Meng Li.

121
00:06:28,399 --> 00:06:29,279
Demon girl?

122
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,560
That dream-eating enchantress

123
00:06:31,199 --> 00:06:32,879
is the last demon in the rumors?

124
00:06:34,759 --> 00:06:36,279
Does Qingdu Temple know about this?

125
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:38,920
Do you remember

126
00:06:38,959 --> 00:06:39,959
the past?

127
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:41,720
What past?

128
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,000
Nothing.

129
00:06:44,639 --> 00:06:45,920
I'll tell Master

130
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:46,879
about Meng Li becoming a demon.

131
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,839
But he's weak from injuries

132
00:06:48,839 --> 00:06:50,000
and can't fight her.

133
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,519
I just heard

134
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,160
her demonic nature is not mature yet.

135
00:06:53,519 --> 00:06:55,519
Now is the best time to kill her.

136
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,360
But

137
00:06:57,759 --> 00:06:59,519
there is a barrier in the Demon Village.

138
00:06:59,879 --> 00:07:01,839
I'm afraid we need to find a way to open it.

139
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,360
Where there is a barrier,

140
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,759
there must be a guardian artifact.

141
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:06,879
Your Highness should pay attention to the holy object in the Demon Village.

142
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,839
This object cannot leave the Demon Village.

143
00:07:09,199 --> 00:07:12,160
In a hidden place, there will be a lion-like Suanni pattern.

144
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:14,000
Find the guardian artifact,

145
00:07:14,519 --> 00:07:16,120
you'll find the way to break it.

146
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,160
Got it.

147
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,639
I see you left food for me.

148
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,839
But I'm not used to eating alone.

149
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,079
Can we

150
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,319
share?

151
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:53,839
I apologize for

152
00:07:53,839 --> 00:07:54,759
my earlier rudeness.

153
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:56,160
It's because

154
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,759
I can't remember the past,

155
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,319
so I'm a bit scared.

156
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,040
I hope

157
00:08:01,279 --> 00:08:01,920
please forgive me.

158
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:05,120
You know I'm a demon hunter,

159
00:08:05,519 --> 00:08:06,759
yet you didn't guard against me,

160
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,160
even healed my wounds.

161
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,360
Do we

162
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,439
have a shared past?

163
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,199
We indeed

164
00:08:14,839 --> 00:08:16,519
have a deep history,

165
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,399
but there's no rush.

166
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:19,639
We have all the time in the world.

167
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:21,800
Very well.

168
00:08:22,439 --> 00:08:23,720
Then I'll join you

169
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:24,839
to retrieve our memories.

170
00:08:37,639 --> 00:08:38,840
Are you looking for something?

171
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,240
Don't get me wrong.

172
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,440
I'm just curious about the items

173
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,840
of the Demon Clan.

174
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,279
Shen Que,

175
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,879
do you know that outside the village,

176
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,840
the demon hunters from Qingdu Temple are after you?

177
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,559
You must stay in the village,

178
00:09:03,039 --> 00:09:04,159
or I won't be able to protect you.

179
00:09:07,919 --> 00:09:08,799
[After me?]

180
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:12,840
[Is it because of her?]

181
00:09:13,159 --> 00:09:13,759
Fine,

182
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,519
I'll do as you say.

183
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,840
[You're so good to me.]

184
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,440
[Could we have been...]

185
00:09:25,759 --> 00:09:26,960
[a couple?]

186
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,440
[These eyes...]

187
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:36,240
[I feel like I've seen them before...]

188
00:09:37,279 --> 00:09:38,399
[That's impossible.]

189
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:53,759
Are you done staring?

190
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:56,519
You don't use a sword,

191
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,639
so why do you have this?

192
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:01,960
Your Highness,

193
00:10:02,679 --> 00:10:04,320
aren't you overstepping?

194
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:07,559
A'Li!

195
00:10:08,159 --> 00:10:09,480
A'Li, what's wrong?

196
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,159
Nothing.

197
00:10:14,759 --> 00:10:15,840
Nothing?

198
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,919
Then why the big noise?

199
00:10:20,039 --> 00:10:21,000
Your Highness,

200
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,840
if you have no other tricks,

201
00:10:22,879 --> 00:10:24,279
please leave.

202
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:40,480
[This cannot leave the Demon Village.]

203
00:10:40,759 --> 00:10:44,000
[Look for a lion-like Suanni pattern.]

204
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,799
[Find the guardian artifact,]

205
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,720
[you'll find the way to break it.]

206
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,399
Your Highness,

207
00:10:58,399 --> 00:10:59,720
we've got news from the Demon Village.

208
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,960
We've found the guardian.

209
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:02,840
Today,

210
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,559
we'll avenge our fallen brothers

211
00:11:04,679 --> 00:11:05,720
and destroy the village.

212
00:11:06,279 --> 00:11:07,720
The demons are cunning.

213
00:11:07,759 --> 00:11:09,360
Don't act rashly.

214
00:11:09,639 --> 00:11:10,960
When the barrier is down,

215
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:12,159
we'll charge in

216
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,919
and avenge our fallen brothers.

217
00:11:14,639 --> 00:11:15,720
All disciples, on my mark!

218
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,120
March!

219
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,159
Yes, sir!

220
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,000
I sense killing intent!

221
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:34,600
This is bad!

222
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:51,759
Your demon power is weak.

223
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,240
Why bother resisting?

224
00:11:53,879 --> 00:11:56,159
You won't be coming back from this!
